{
  "video_id": "D96OZkx2bOs",
  "title": "Giving Artists With Disabilities a Space to Thrive",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 197.0,
      "end_time": 2780.0,
      "text": "(gentle music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9340.0,
      "end_time": 10960.0,
      "text": "- I remember my first experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10960.0,
      "end_time": 14280.0,
      "text": "of seeing this amazing production of art"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14280.0,
      "end_time": 16300.0,
      "text": "that was different than what I had seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16300.0,
      "end_time": 17770.0,
      "text": "and it was such a personal expression"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17770.0,
      "end_time": 19200.0,
      "text": "by the person making it."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19200.0,
      "end_time": 20950.0,
      "text": "They may or may not have had language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20950.0,
      "end_time": 23530.0,
      "text": "they may or may not been able to communicate with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23530.0,
      "end_time": 24530.0,
      "text": "but they're making this work."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24530.0,
      "end_time": 27603.0,
      "text": "That's really a window into their soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29900.0,
      "end_time": 32159.0,
      "text": "When you ask someone who's been disenfranchised"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 35360.0,
      "text": "their entire life to tell me your story"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35360.0,
      "end_time": 37330.0,
      "text": "it's amazing how the door opens."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43133.0,
      "end_time": 46300.0,
      "text": "(upbeat violin music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53550.0,
      "end_time": 55629.0,
      "text": "Creative Growth Art Center is the oldest and largest"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55630.0,
      "end_time": 58610.0,
      "text": "center for artists with disabilities in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58610.0,
      "end_time": 62240.0,
      "text": "When we were founded, the idea of disability, then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62240.0,
      "end_time": 65530.0,
      "text": "was so radically different than what it is now."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65530.0,
      "end_time": 67490.0,
      "text": "We didn't come out of a hospital setting"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67490.0,
      "end_time": 70369.0,
      "text": "or we didn't come out of a vocational training program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70370.0,
      "end_time": 72700.0,
      "text": "we came out of some artists getting together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72700.0,
      "end_time": 76310.0,
      "text": "in a home in Oakland, putting paint on a table in the garage"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76310.0,
      "end_time": 78170.0,
      "text": "and just saying, this is what artists do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78170.0,
      "end_time": 80983.0,
      "text": "and this is how we can change the social fabric."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85270.0,
      "end_time": 87259.0,
      "text": "From those, kind of, humble beginnings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90630.0,
      "text": "we now serve 162 artists with disabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90630.0,
      "end_time": 92720.0,
      "text": "in our studio, every week."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92720.0,
      "end_time": 94140.0,
      "text": "It's a very big space."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94140.0,
      "end_time": 97710.0,
      "text": "Within that, you'll find almost every possible expression"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97710.0,
      "end_time": 98979.0,
      "text": "of visual art."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98980.0,
      "end_time": 101220.0,
      "text": "You'll see the rug making area, the wood shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101220.0,
      "end_time": 103480.0,
      "text": "the ceramic studio, the fashion area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103480.0,
      "end_time": 104890.0,
      "text": "the painting and drawing area"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104890.0,
      "end_time": 106240.0,
      "text": "and everyone's working together"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106240.0,
      "end_time": 108610.0,
      "text": "and everyone can see each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108610.0,
      "end_time": 110320.0,
      "text": "It's different than most places"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110320.0,
      "end_time": 113740.0,
      "text": "and some people don't believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113740.0,
      "end_time": 116470.0,
      "text": "Some people think, like, you must have doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116470.0,
      "end_time": 118700.0,
      "text": "and you must have all these other things"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118700.0,
      "end_time": 120300.0,
      "text": "and how do you deal with the studio everyday."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120300.0,
      "end_time": 123262.0,
      "text": "It's like, no, you know, art is the common language."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124130.0,
      "end_time": 126390.0,
      "text": "And a lot of our folks don't verbalize or speak"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126390.0,
      "end_time": 127600.0,
      "text": "or they speak sign language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127600.0,
      "end_time": 130200.0,
      "text": "but art is the language that moves us forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 136670.0,
      "text": "- This is called the Oil Red Sea Number One."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136670.0,
      "end_time": 138773.0,
      "text": "Red is the only color I can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140520.0,
      "end_time": 143140.0,
      "text": "- [Tom] You look at work of an artist like Dan Miller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143140.0,
      "end_time": 144630.0,
      "text": "ya know, he's pretty much non-verbal."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144630.0,
      "end_time": 147100.0,
      "text": "His mother tried to encourage him to speak"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147100.0,
      "end_time": 149859.0,
      "text": "by telling him how to spell words when he was a boy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149860.0,
      "end_time": 151140.0,
      "text": "every night, and he never spoke them"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 151140.0,
      "end_time": 153214.0,
      "text": "until he started to draw them."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153214.0,
      "end_time": 156400.0,
      "text": "- A light goes click, click, click."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158653.0,
      "end_time": 161170.0,
      "text": "- [Tom] Look at an artist like Monica Valentine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161170.0,
      "end_time": 165579.0,
      "text": "she takes pins and she takes sequins and colored beads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165580.0,
      "end_time": 167400.0,
      "text": "and she strings those together on the pin"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167400.0,
      "end_time": 169830.0,
      "text": "and she puts them into styrofoam forms"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169830.0,
      "end_time": 172723.0,
      "text": "to form these optically charged sculptures."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173600.0,
      "end_time": 177440.0,
      "text": "When you realize that Monica has prosthetic eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177440.0,
      "end_time": 180410.0,
      "text": "and can't see color or see anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180410.0,
      "end_time": 182793.0,
      "text": "it moves into this whole other range."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184300.0,
      "end_time": 186980.0,
      "text": "We want their own voice, we want it as pure"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186980.0,
      "end_time": 189350.0,
      "text": "and personalized as it can be."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189350.0,
      "end_time": 192950.0,
      "text": "And 45 years later, it continues to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 192950.0,
      "end_time": 195478.0,
      "text": "How's that building coming along, Pete?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 195479.0,
      "end_time": 197290.0,
      "text": "- Slowly. - It's looking good."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202420.0,
      "end_time": 204850.0,
      "text": "The record of success that Creative Growth has"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204850.0,
      "end_time": 206810.0,
      "text": "is phenomenal, it's off the charts"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 206810.0,
      "end_time": 208790.0,
      "text": "in terms of what an art school"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208790.0,
      "end_time": 210440.0,
      "text": "or any other, sort of, enterprise"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210440.0,
      "end_time": 212363.0,
      "text": "would consider to be acceptable."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213280.0,
      "end_time": 216340.0,
      "text": "We have three artists with work in the Museum of Modern Art"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216340.0,
      "end_time": 217460.0,
      "text": "permanent collection in New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217460.0,
      "end_time": 219920.0,
      "text": "in the San Francisco Museum of Modern Art collection."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 219920.0,
      "end_time": 222239.0,
      "text": "And, this year, we have the first two people"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222240.0,
      "end_time": 223570.0,
      "text": "with developmental disabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 223570.0,
      "end_time": 225700.0,
      "text": "they have work in the Venice Bienalle."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 225700.0,
      "end_time": 228880.0,
      "text": "The Venice Bienalle is the most important, prestigious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228880.0,
      "end_time": 231493.0,
      "text": "by invitation-only exhibition in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232650.0,
      "end_time": 234190.0,
      "text": "Their work is sought after."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 234190.0,
      "end_time": 236770.0,
      "text": "Ya know, a piece is done, and there's a waiting list."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 236770.0,
      "end_time": 238940.0,
      "text": "Rosina, I haven't even said hello to you, yet, today."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 238940.0,
      "end_time": 239940.0,
      "text": "- How are you? - Good."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239940.0,
      "end_time": 241829.0,
      "text": "To be able to work at a place like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 241830.0,
      "end_time": 244530.0,
      "text": "is beyond anything I had hoped for."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 244900.0,
      "end_time": 247627.0,
      "text": "I get to work with phenomenally talented people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247627.0,
      "end_time": 251160.0,
      "text": "and to see how they negotiate the day everyday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 251160.0,
      "end_time": 255130.0,
      "text": "how they get around obstacles, how they continue to say yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 255130.0,
      "end_time": 256600.0,
      "text": "when everyone is telling them no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 256600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 257570.00000000003,
      "text": "that's an amazing thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 257570.0,
      "end_time": 260623.0,
      "text": "That's a life lesson I get reminded of every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 261526.0,
      "end_time": 264193.0,
      "text": "(gentle music)"
    }
  ]
}